node.text:
Had such an amazing time speaking at the Kroger Wellness Experience representing @drinkorro in Cincinnati 🎉 
Thankful for this experience and all the safety precautions taken during this time.  Can’t wait to get back to Cincinnati! Also Orro is back in stock with lower sodium and an even better taste! 
DrinkOrro.com
#drinkorro #forthehungry #orro_partner #tabithabrown
📸 by @4philanthropy

node.text: Who remembers this episode??? Honey this was one of the funniest Fridays with Tab and Chance moments😂. We can’t wait to get back to y’all real soon!! Until then, enjoy this memory and good laugh with us!  Love y’all! #fridayswithtabandchance #tabithabrown #chancebrown

node.text:
I have been laughing and reminiscing for the last hour after watching this 😂😂. My granny was a channel 8 “All My Children” Erica Kane watcher tho, she wouldn’t even watch Y&R😂😂 “The stories” is what we call em😂. She said you had to make a choice😂😂 But everything else is spot on!! Who else has these memories?? Let me go find me a piece strawberry candy😂 #memorylane #hilarious #truth
@relltheremedy thank you for this 😂😂

node.text:
4 years ago I was driving Uber and would often drop people off at the Van Nuys Airport for their private flights.  Today, God said it was my turn!! 
🙌🏿OOHH GOD I THANK YOU🙌🏿 
I feel so blessed to be on this journey and to share this moment with my baby girl, makes it even more special! Dreams that I never even imagined are coming true!! Can’t wait to share what we are working on together 🙌🏿❤️ Something special coming soon!! #ThankyouGod #tabithabrown #choycebrown #motherdaughter
